								<div class="title" id="post-title-4716512">
																		
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/norimori" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1222161); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1222161&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610183042" alt="NoriMori" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1222161)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/norimori" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1222161); return false;" >NoriMori</a></span> <span class="odate time_1594515785 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">12 Jul 2020 01:03</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4716512">
									

<p>The pipes grow when not under observation. When he blinks, he's not observing them. That's why it's dangerous to sleep, and why it moves slowly enough that it doesn't kill him when he's asleep.</p>
<p>The face bit was a bit of a stretch though, as was calling it a &quot;monster&quot;. While it's true the pipes can be made of things like human flesh, and that someone in this guy's position might call a mass of growing pipes &quot;a monster&quot;, that part was just a bit too misleading and just doesn't ring true.</p>

							</div>

								
